OOC: Banzai-Tron never fired on Trinity, LegendaryNemasis.  The only person 
he fired on is Nightlight.

:::Sharpedge/Banzai-Tron:::

::Sharpedge gets hit by about half of the energy balls. He dodged the disks.  
He fires another two missles at Nightlight::
~~~~~
::Banzai-Tron tries to dodge the energy balls, but a couple of them hit him. 
He was hit by 1 of the disks, the other one zooming off.  He fired 2 missles 
at Nightlight.  It was about that time when he was hit by one of the Matrix 
blasts. He fell over backwards, not in stasis lock, but hurt bad::

--part1_10.f294d36.28787cbc_boundary
